{
  "page": "Alyssa Arryn",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\"><img alt=\"House Arryn.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/50px-House_Arryn.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/75px-House_Arryn.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/100px-House_Arryn.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Alyssa Arryn</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\"><img alt=\"House Arryn.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/50px-House_Arryn.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/75px-House_Arryn.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/100px-House_Arryn.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Marc_simonetti_bronnandvardis.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Marc simonetti bronnandvardis.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5b/Marc_simonetti_bronnandvardis.jpg/350px-Marc_simonetti_bronnandvardis.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"532\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5b/Marc_simonetti_bronnandvardis.jpg/525px-Marc_simonetti_bronnandvardis.jpg 1.5x, /images/5/5b/Marc_simonetti_bronnandvardis.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Vardis_Egen\" title=\"Vardis Egen\">Vardis Egen</a> duels <a href=\"/index.php/Bronn\" title=\"Bronn\">Bronn</a> near the statue of Alyssa Arryn, by Marc Simonetti ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">House Arryn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Valemen\" title=\"Valemen\">Valemen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Alyssa Arryn</b> is a half-legendary figure of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">House Arryn</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Alyssa%27s_Tears\" title=\"Alyssa&#39;s Tears\">Alyssa's Tears</a>, a waterfall in the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">Vale of Arryn</a>, is <a href=\"/index.php/Named_for\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Named for\">named for</a> her.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Statue_of_Alyssa\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Statue of Alyssa</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alyssa_Arryn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">Maesters</a> are reasonably certain that Alyssa Arryn did exist, but are not exactly sure when she lived. Most people believe her to have lived six thousand years ago,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> but the book <i><a href=\"/index.php/True_History\" title=\"True History\">True History</a></i> states four thousand years ago. Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Denestan\" title=\"Denestan\">Denestan</a>, in his <i><a href=\"/index.php/Questions\" title=\"Questions\">Questions</a></i>, states two thousand years.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf742_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf742-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> According to legend, Alyssa saw her husband, her brothers, and her children killed in front of her, but she did not shed a tear. As a consequence, after her own death, the <a href=\"/index.php/Gods\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Gods\">gods</a> determined that she would not know rest until her tears reached the earth of the Vale of Arryn, where all those she had loved were buried. The waterfall that flows from the <a href=\"/index.php/Giant%27s_Lance\" title=\"Giant&#39;s Lance\">Giant's Lance</a>, known as <a href=\"/index.php/Alyssa%27s_Tears\" title=\"Alyssa&#39;s Tears\">Alyssa's Tears</a>, pours from such a height that the water turns into mist and is dispersed by wind before it ever reaches the ground below. Per the legend, no drop of the waterfall has ever reached the valley.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf742_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf742-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Statue_of_Alyssa\">Statue of Alyssa</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alyssa_Arryn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Statue of Alyssa\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Felicia_Cano_i_fight_to_win.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/57/Felicia_Cano_i_fight_to_win.JPG/400px-Felicia_Cano_i_fight_to_win.JPG\" width=\"400\" height=\"167\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/57/Felicia_Cano_i_fight_to_win.JPG/600px-Felicia_Cano_i_fight_to_win.JPG 1.5x, /images/5/57/Felicia_Cano_i_fight_to_win.JPG 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Felicia_Cano_i_fight_to_win.JPG\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Alyssa's statue is pushed by <a href=\"/index.php/Bronn\" title=\"Bronn\">Bronn</a>. © FFG</div></div></div>\n<p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Godswood_of_the_Eyrie\" title=\"Godswood of the Eyrie\">godswood of the Eyrie</a> includes a woman's statue, located at its center. It depicts a weeping woman, carved in veined white <a href=\"/index.php/Marble\" title=\"Marble\">marble</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a> felt certain that it was a statue of Alyssa.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alyssa_Arryn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alyssa_Arryn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>The duel between Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Vardis_Egen\" title=\"Vardis Egen\">Vardis Egen</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Bronn\" title=\"Bronn\">Bronn</a> takes place by Alyssa's statue. Early in the duel, Bronn hides behind the statue of the weeping woman. A failed lunge by Ser Vardis results in his sword striking the marble thigh of \"Alyssa\". Later, an off-balance Bronn gets hold of the statue to avoid falling to the ground. A wounded Ser Vardis chooses the moment to attack, but Bronn is able to avoid the strike. As a result, Ser Vardis's sword strikes the elbow of the statue and breaks. Bronn then pushes the back of the statue, breaking its torso. The heavy piece of marble falls on Ser Vardis and traps him beneath it, allowing Bronn to easily kill the incapacitated <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alyssa_Arryn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:MKomarck_SansaEyrie.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/97/MKomarck_SansaEyrie.jpg/350px-MKomarck_SansaEyrie.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"310\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/97/MKomarck_SansaEyrie.jpg/525px-MKomarck_SansaEyrie.jpg 1.5x, /images/9/97/MKomarck_SansaEyrie.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:MKomarck_SansaEyrie.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Godswood_of_the_Eyrie\" title=\"Godswood of the Eyrie\">godswood of the Eyrie</a>, with the broken statue of Alyssa behind her, by Michael Komarck ©</div></div></div>\n<p>Snow falls upon the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a> enters the godswood and notices a broken statue of a weeping woman lying on the ground in the center of the garden, half-buried by snow. She builds a snow castle copy of <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a> nearby.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alyssa_Arryn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Alyssa had been dead six thousand years now, and still no drop of <a href=\"/index.php/Alyssa%27s_Tears\" title=\"Alyssa&#39;s Tears\">the torrent</a> had ever reached the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">valley floor</a> far below. Catelyn wondered how large a waterfall her own tears would make when she died.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alyssa_Arryn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Category:Images_of_Alyssa_Arryn\" title=\"Category:Images of Alyssa Arryn\">Images of Alyssa Arryn</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alyssa_Arryn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\">1.5</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_40\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 40\">Chapter 40</a>, Catelyn VII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf742-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf742_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf742_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Seven Kingdoms&#58; The Vale&#32;(The Eyrie).</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_80\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 80\">Chapter 80</a>, Sansa VII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403232043\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.090 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.300 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1007/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10818/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 8897/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1120/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2844/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.190/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.46 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  280.901      1 -total\n 93.90%  263.761      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 93.44%  262.467      1 Template:Infobox\n  9.33%   26.218     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  4.70%   13.204      9 Template:Ref\n  3.21%    9.015      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  2.59%    7.278      9 Template:Ref/core\n  0.88%    2.478      1 Template:References\n  0.66%    1.865      1 Template:Quote\n  0.45%    1.270      2 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:2720-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403232042 and revision id 323650\n -->\n",
